name: Pothole Fork of Woody
description:
Introduction

More technically challenging than main Woody. Features two real keepers. All anchors are sandtrap or pack drag. Please use LNT retrievable anchors and keep it this way. If you have any trouble in main fork stay out of pothole fork.
